'''guinea pig''' (''plural'' '''guinea pigs''')

#A tailless [[rodent]] of the ''[[Cavia]]'' genus, with short [[ear]]s and larger than a [[hamster]]; the species ''[[Cavia porcellus]]'' is often kept as a [[pet]].
#{{idiom}} A [[person]] who volunteers for an [[experiment]] or to try anything new; an experimental subject (''from the use of the rodent in laboratory experiments'').
